description:
Rewrapped - Season 1, Episode 6




Let's Get Ready to Crumble!

The Rewrappers reach into the cookie jar and pull out morsels of fun in the Recreate Challenge when they take on the Entenmann's Original Recipe Chocolate Chip Cookie! They must then use the chewy, chocolaty treat in an original dish in the Innovate Challenge. The judges will determine which dish is just cookie-cutter and which Rewrapper is the smartest cookie of them all!




Original Air Date: 19-May-2014
